org.moeaframework.util.weights
Interface WeightGenerator

All Known Implementing Classes:
NormalBoundaryIntersectionGenerator, RandomGenerator, UniformDesignGenerator
public interface WeightGenerator

Interface for generating a sequence of weights. The nature of the weights depends on the specific implementation. The only requirement is that the sum of each component in a weight vector be 1.

Method Summary

          Returns the generated weights.
